I"=<h3><span class="cooper">Comedy</span> scenes made up on the spot</h3>
<h3>Based on suggestions made by <span class="cooper">you</span></h3>

<p>The Shambles are a short form improvised comedy troupe founded in 2006 at the University of York by a member of <a href="https://www.oxfordimps.com/"> The Oxford Imps </a>. Over the years, their reputation evolved and they have become one of the most loved improv troupes at the Edinburgh Fringe.</p>

<p>They perform a range of songs, scenes and games based entirely on your suggestions. Performing throughout the entire Fringe and regularly around York, there’s always a chance to catch the fast wit of The Shambles.</p>

<p>Also, they’re called The Shambles after <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Shambles">this famous road in York.</a> Not because they are bad.</p>
